# shapeShift
## Description
An app to keep track of your wellness routines and connect to a fitness community

## Installation
No installation needed, just login to the website and start your fitness journey.

## Usage

![image](./photo/shapeshift_ex2.PNG)

![image](./photo/shapeshift_ex1.PNG)
This appliction allows you to keep track of your fitness/wellness routines, Calculate your BMr, total Daily Energy Expenditure, Caloric needs, Ideal body weight all while logging/tracking past work outs that you enjoyed and might want to remember for the future. 
Use this application freely but bear with us because its still a work in progress.  If you want to Gain mass, lose some weight or work out and still remain the same size but just tone up, we got you covered with shapeShift!
